%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Predicted%20XI%20vs%20NZ%3A%20Will%20Rohit%20Tinker%20With%20Winning%20Combination%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20will%20face%20off%20in%20the%20semi-finals%20of%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20November%2015%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20IND%20vs%20NZ%20match%20starts%20at%202%3A00%20PM%20IST.%20India%20steamrolled%20opponents%20during%20the%20league%20stage%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20clinching%20victories%20in%20all%20nine%20league%20matches%20and%20securing%20the%20top%20spot%20on%20the%20points%20table.%20The%20team's%20exceptional%20performance%20has%20been%20highlighted%20by%20a%20formidable%20batting%20lineup%20and%20a%20lethal%20bowling%20attack%2C%20proving%20effective%20on%20flat%20tracks%20as%20well%20as%20on%20slow-turning%20surfaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpeners%3A%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20led%20the%20team%20from%20the%20front%20at%20this%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20setting%20a%20strong%20foundation%20for%20the%20team%20with%20brisk%20starts%20at%20the%20top.%20His%20aggressive%20approach%20has%20eased%20pressure%20on%20the%20middle%20order.%20With%20503%20runs%20in%20nine%20matches%2C%20the%20right-handed%20batter%20has%20notched%20up%20one%20century%20and%20three%20half-centuries%2C%20with%20a%20highest%20score%20of%20131.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20opening%20partner%2C%20may%20not%20have%20fully%20unleashed%20his%20potential%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%20he%20has%20effectively%20supported%20the%20captain%20in%20initiating%20the%20innings%20briskly.%20Despite%20returning%20from%20illness%2C%20the%20right-handed%20batter%20has%20scored%20270%20runs%20in%20seven%20matches%2C%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20104.65.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMiddle%20order%3A%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20594%20runs%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20has%20established%20himself%20as%20the%20most%20prolific%20run-scorer%20in%20the%20tournament%20so%20far.%20In%20nine%20matches%2C%20Kohli%20has%20demonstrated%20consistent%20run-scoring%20abilities%20while%20dropping%20anchor%20in%20challenging%20situations.%20The%20right-handed%20batter%20has%20scored%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2099%20in%20the%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreyas%20Iyer%20and%20KL%20Rahul%20have%20been%20crucial%20in%20strengthening%20India's%20middle%20order.%20Iyer's%20aggressive%20mindset%20has%20seen%20him%20take%20the%20attack%20to%20the%20opposition%2C%20while%20KL%20Rahul%20has%20adopted%20a%20measured%20approach%20while%20constructing%20his%20innings.%20Iyer%20has%20scored%20421%20runs%20in%20nine%20matches%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20106.58%2C%20while%20KL%20Rahul%20has%20notched%20up%20347%20runs%20in%20the%20same%20number%20of%20matches.%20Both%20batters%20will%20enter%20the%20upcoming%20match%20with%20the%20confidence%20of%20having%20scored%20centuries%20against%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20limited%20opportunities%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20opposition%20with%20his%20explosive%20batting%20prowess.%20The%20upcoming%20knockout%20games%20could%20provide%20an%20ideal%20platform%20for%20the%20right-handed%20batter%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20impact%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll-rounders%3A%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%20has%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20Team%20India's%20dominating%20performance%20in%20the%20tournament.%20The%20left-arm%20spinner's%20skill%20in%20maintaining%20control%20over%20the%20run%20rate%20and%20securing%20crucial%20breakthroughs%20during%20the%20middle%20overs%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20displayed%20once%20again%20in%20the%20upcoming%20match.%20In%20nine%20games%2C%20Jadeja%20has%20claimed%2016%20wickets%20with%20the%20best%20figures%20of%205%2F33.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBowlers%3A%20Mohammad%20Shami%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20Mohammed%20Siraj%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20have%20established%20a%20formidable%20partnership%2C%20consistently%20delivering%20early%20breakthroughs%20with%20the%20new%20ball.%20Leading%20the%20wicket-taking%20charts%20for%20India%20in%20the%20competition%2C%20Bumrah%20has%20secured%2017%20wickets%2C%20while%20Siraj%20has%20contributed%20with%2012%20dismissals%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20potent%20force%20with%20the%20new%20ball%20as%20well%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%2C%20consistently%20delivering%20crucial%20breakthroughs%20while%20effectively%20controlling%20the%20opposition's%20run%20rate.%20The%20right-arm%20pacer%20has%20bagged%2016%20wickets%20in%20five%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20a%20key%20asset%20for%20India%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%20throughout%20the%20tournament%2C%20has%20secured%2014%20wickets%20in%20nine%20matches.%20The%20left-arm%20chinaman%20bowler%20is%20expected%20to%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20restraining%20the%20big-hitters%20of%20the%20Kiwi%20team%20in%20the%20upcoming%20semi-final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Predicted%20Playing%20XI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20(c)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKL%20Rahul%20(wk)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Shami%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Siraj%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700014260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F8809k3o8_sha