0Diwali%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region.%20Fireworks%2C%20one%20of%20the%20causes%20behind%20pollution%20along%20with%20stubble%20burning%20and%20vehicular%20emissions%2C%20continue%20in%20violation%20of%20a%20court%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Air%20quality%20across%20Delhi%20continues%20to%20be%20in%20the%20'Severe'%20category%20as%20per%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(Visuals%20from%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20shot%20at%206%3A30%20am)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAxgNPrXBOv%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FAxgNPrXBOv%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1724600721612607562%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20air%20quality%20index%20(AQI)%2C%20which%20measures%20pollution%20in%20the%20air%2C%20was%20recorded%20in%20the%20'severe'%20category%20in%20most%20places%20in%20the%20city%20this%20morning%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AQI%20was%20recorded%20at%20417%20in%20RK%20Puram%2C%20430%20in%20Anand%20Vihar%2C%20403%20at%20IGI%20airport%2C%20430%20in%20Narela%2C%20and%20423%20in%20Punjabi%20Bagh%2C%20showed%20data%20recorded%20by%20the%20CPCB%20at%206%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AQI%20between%20zero%20and%2050%20is%20considered%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%2C%2051%20and%20100%20%26quot%3Bsatisfactory%26quot%3B%2C%20101%20and%20200%20%26quot%3Bmoderate%26quot%3B%2C%20201%20and%20300%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%2C%20301%20and%20400%20%26quot%3Bvery%20poor%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20401%20and%20500%20%26quot%3Bsevere%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20an%20AQI%20level%20of%20400-500%20impacts%20healthy%20people%20and%20seriously%20impacts%20those%20with%20existing%20diseases%2C%20an%20AQI%20level%20of%20301-400%20causes%20respiratory%20illness%20on%20prolonged%20exposure.%20An%20AQI%20level%20of%20201-300%20and%20150-200%20may%20bring%20discomfort%20to%20people%20with%20lungs%2C%20asthma%2C%20and%20heart%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20quality%20in%20Delhi%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20north%20India%20deteriorates%20every%20year%20ahead%20of%20winter%20when%20cold%20air%20traps%20pollutants%20from%20vehicles%2C%20industry%2C%20construction%20dust%2C%20and%20stubble%20burning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20was%20cloaked%20in%20a%20thick%20blanket%20of%20smog%20with%20severe%20pollution%20levels%20for%20a%20week%20since%20October%2028%2C%20prompting%20the%20government%20to%20shut%20schools%20and%20ban%20diesel%20trucks.%20Rain%20last%20week%20provided%20some%20respite%20but%20the%20improvement%20was%20wiped%20out%20as%20the%20smoke%20from%20firecrackers%20on%20Diwali%20added%20to%20the%20air%20pollution%20due%20to%20stubble%20burning%20in%20north%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700012160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fel81ueh_delhi-pollution-nov-15-2023_625x300_15_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-air-quality-still-severe-in-delhi-as-rain-remains-elusive-since-diwali-4574840%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20air%20quality%20remains%20'severe'%20at%20most%20places%20in%20Delhi%20as%20the%20pollution%20crisis%20returned%20to%20the%20national%20capital%20following%20Diwali%2C%20wiping%20out%20the%20improvements%20recorded%20due%20to%20rain%20last%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-air-quality-still-severe-in-delhi-as-rain-remains-elusive-since-diwali-4574840%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.amppr