26quot%3Bprecise%20and%20targeted%20operation%20against%20Hamas%20in%20a%20specified%20area%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20facility%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20site%20of%20a%20standoff%20with%20the%20ruling%20militant%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20authorities%20claim%20the%20militants%20conceal%20military%20operations%20in%20the%20Al%20Shifa%20Hospital.%20But%20with%20hundreds%20of%20patients%20and%20medical%20personnel%20inside%2C%20the%20military%20has%20refrained%20from%20entering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20Israeli%20defense%20forces%20have%20publicly%20warned%20that%20such%20use%20of%20the%20hospital%20%26quot%3Bjeopardizes%20its%20protected%20status%20under%20international%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20military%20said.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20military%20officials%20conveyed%20again%20to%20Gaza%20authorities%20that%20all%20military%20activity%20in%20the%20hospital%20must%20cease%20within%2012%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20it%20did%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20military%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20denied%20the%20Israeli%20accusations%20that%20it%20uses%20the%20hospital%20for%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoctors%20at%20the%20hospital%20told%20CNN%20that%20they%20were%20given%2030%20minutes%20of%20warning%20before%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20asked%20to%20stay%20clear%20of%20the%20windows%20and%20the%20balconies%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Khaled%20Abu%20Samra%20told%20CNN.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20hear%20the%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20they%20are%20very%20close%20to%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20complex.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20military%20officials%20gave%20no%20further%20details%20but%20said%20they%20were%20taking%20steps%20to%20avoid%20harm%20to%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20unfolded%20after%20the%20military%20seized%20broader%20control%20of%20northern%20Gaza%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20including%20capturing%20the%20territory's%20legislature%20building%20and%20its%20police%20headquarters%2C%20in%20gains%20that%20carried%20high%20symbolic%20value%20in%20the%20country's%20quest%20to%20crush%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%F0%9F%94%B4%20Operational%20Update%3A%3Cbr%3EIDF%20forces%20are%20carrying%20out%20a%20precise%20and%20targeted%20operation%20against%20Hamas%20in%20a%20specified%20area%20in%20the%20Shifa%20Hospital%2C%20based%20on%20intelligence%20information%20and%20an%20operational%20necessity.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20IDF%20is%20conducting%20a%20ground%20operation%20in%20Gaza%20to%20defeat%20Hamas%20and%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(%40IDF)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIDF%2Fstatus%2F1724579353193754958%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAhead%20of%20the%20operation%2C%20we%20made%20an%20effort%20to%20evacuate%20the%20hospital%20from%20its%20patients%20and%20even%20opened%20a%20specific%20safe%20passage%20from%20the%20hospital.%20We%20notified%20the%20hospital's%20management%20ahead%20of%20the%20entry%20into%20the%20compound%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IDF%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoctors%20this%20week%20have%20pleaded%20for%20assistance%20amid%20failing%20power%20at%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20electricity.%20There's%20no%20water%20in%20the%20hospital.%20There's%20no%20food.%20People%20will%20die%20in%20a%20few%20hours%20without%20functioning%20ventilators%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20doctor%20with%20the%20international%20humanitarian%20group%20Doctors%20Without%20Borders%20said%20in%20a%20Monday%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FMSF_canada%2Fstatus%2F1724089175517901171%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAl%20Shifa%20Hospital%20is%20one%20of%20at%20least%20four%20major%20hospitals%20in%20Gaza%20that%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20the%20front%20line%20of%20fighting%20in%20recent%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThousands%2C%20including%20doctors%2C%20patients%2C%20and%20those%20who%20fled%20their%20homes%2C%20are%20said%20to%20be%20sheltering%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternational%20organizations%20have%20warned%20of%20crises%20at%20multiple%20medical%20facilities%2C%20including%20Al%20Shifa%2C%20which%20is%20the%20biggest%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesperson%20John%20Kirby%20said%20the%20US%20has%20unspecified%20intelligence%20that%20Hamas%20and%20other%20Palestinian%20militants%20use%20Shifa%20and%20other%20hospitals%20and%20tunnels%20underneath%20them%20to%20support%20military%20operations%20and%20hold%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story.%20Check%20back%20for%20updates.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-military-says-its-forces-have-entered-gaza-shifa-hospital-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700009884000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655412944ca513d8242993e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-military-says-its-forces-have-entered-gaza-shifa-hospital-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22International%20organizations%20have%20warned%20of%20crises%20at%20multiple%20medical%20facilities%2C%20including%20Shifa%20Hospital%2C%20which%20is%20the%20largest%20in%20Gaza%20City.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Snodgrass%2CAssociated%20Press)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-military-says-its-forces-have-entered-