efore%20will%20take%20infectious%20diseases%20with%20them%2C%20and%20health%20systems%20will%20struggle%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20burden%2C%20the%20researchers%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dire%20assessment%20comes%20during%20what%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20hottest%20year%20in%20human%20history%20--%20just%20last%20week%2C%20Europe's%20climate%20monitor%20declared%20that%20last%20month%20was%20the%20warmest%20October%20on%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%20COP28%20climate%20talks%20in%20Dubai%20later%20this%20month%2C%20which%20will%20for%20the%20first%20time%20host%20a%20%26quot%3Bhealth%20day%26quot%3B%20on%20December%203%20as%20experts%20try%20to%20shine%20a%20light%20on%20global%20warming's%20impact%20on%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20growing%20calls%20for%20global%20action%2C%20energy-related%20carbon%20emissions%20hit%20new%20highs%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Lancet%20Countdown%20report%20said%2C%20singling%20out%20still%20massive%20government%20subsidies%20and%20private%20bank%20investments%20into%20planet-heating%20fossil%20fuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Crisis%20on%20top%20of%20a%20crisis'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20people%20worldwide%20were%20exposed%20to%20an%20average%20of%2086%20days%20of%20life-threatening%20temperatures%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Lancet%20Countdown%20study.%20Around%2060%20percent%20of%20those%20days%20were%20made%20more%20than%20twice%20as%20likely%20due%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20people%20over%2065%20who%20died%20from%20heat%20rose%20by%2085%20percent%20from%201991-2000%20to%202013-2022%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%20these%20impacts%20that%20we%20are%20seeing%20today%20could%20be%20just%20an%20early%20symptom%20of%20a%20very%20dangerous%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Lancet%20Countdown's%20executive%20director%20Marina%20Romanello%20told%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20a%20scenario%20in%20which%20the%20world%20warms%20by%20two%20degrees%20Celsius%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20century%20--%20it%20is%20currently%20on%20track%20for%202.7C%20--%20annual%20heat-related%20deaths%20were%20projected%20to%20increase%20370%20percent%20by%202050.%20That%20marks%20a%204.7-fold%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20520%20million%20more%20people%20will%20experience%20moderate%20or%20severe%20food%20insecurity%20by%20mid-century%2C%20according%20to%20the%20projections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20mosquito-borne%20infectious%20diseases%20will%20continue%20to%20spread%20into%20new%20areas.%20The%20transmission%20of%20dengue%20would%20increase%20by%2036%20percent%20under%20a%202C%20warming%20scenario%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20more%20than%20a%20quarter%20of%20cities%20surveyed%20by%20the%20researchers%20said%20they%20were%20worried%20that%20climate%20change%20would%20overwhelm%20their%20capacity%20to%20cope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20facing%20a%20crisis%20on%20top%20of%20a%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lancet%20Countdown's%20Georgiana%20Gordon-Strachan%2C%20whose%20homeland%20Jamaica%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20dengue%20outbreak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Staring%20down%20the%20barrel'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20living%20in%20poorer%20countries%2C%20who%20are%20often%20least%20responsible%20for%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%2C%20are%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20health%20impacts%2C%20but%20are%20least%20able%20to%20access%20funding%20and%20technical%20capacity%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20deadly%20storms%2C%20rising%20seas%20and%20crop-withering%20droughts%20worsened%20by%20global%20heating%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20responded%20to%20the%20report%20by%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bhumanity%20is%20staring%20down%20the%20barrel%20of%20an%20intolerable%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20already%20seeing%20a%20human%20catastrophe%20unfolding%20with%20the%20health%20and%20livelihoods%20of%20billions%20across%20the%20world%20endangered%20by%20record-breaking%20heat%2C%20crop-failing%20droughts%2C%20rising%20levels%20of%20hunger%2C%20growing%20infectious%20disease%20outbreaks%2C%20and%20deadly%20storms%20and%20floods%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDann%20Mitchell%2C%20climate%20hazards%20chair%20at%20the%20UK's%20Bristol%20University%2C%20lamented%20that%20%26quot%3Balready%20catastrophic%26quot%3B%20health%20warnings%20about%20climate%20change%20had%20%26quot%3Bnot%20managed%20to%20convince%20the%20world's%20governments%20to%20cut%20carbon%20emissions%20enough%20to%20avoid%20the%20first%20Paris%20Agreement%20goal%20of%201.5C%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20warned%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20countries'%20current%20pledges%20will%20cut%20global%20carbon%20emissions%20by%20just%20two%20percent%20by%202030%20from%202019%20levels%20--%20far%20short%20of%20the%2043%20percent%20drop%20needed%20to%20limit%20warming%20to%201.5C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERomanello%20warned%20that%20if%20more%20progress%20is%20not%20made%20on%20emissions%2C%20then%20%26quot%3Bthe%20growing%20emphasis%20on%20health%20within%20climate%20change%20negotiations%20risks%20being%20just%20empty%20words%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700006460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2F4g27a3a_spain-heat-afp_625x300_28_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fheat-projected-to-kill-nearly-five-times-more-people-by-2050-4574783%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%20five%20times%20more%20people%20will%20likely%20die%20due%20to%20extreme%20heat%20i