indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Five-no-doubt-bjp-will-prevail-pm-modi-will-be-back-with-a-bigger-margin-in-2024-amit-shah%2Farticleshow%2F105219533.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20BJP's%20prospects%20in%20the%20upcoming%20state%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%20He%20cited%20anti-incumbency%20against%20Congress%20as%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20these%20states%20and%20highlighted%20BJP's%20positive%20image%20among%20the%20people.%20Shah%20also%20predicted%20a%20comfortable%20win%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20He%20addressed%20concerns%20about%20BJP's%20loss%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20assured%20that%20the%20party%20would%20regain%20its%20popularity%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22AKHILESH%20SINGH%20AND%20DIWAKAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Five-no-doubt-bjp-will-prevail-pm-modi-will-be-back-with-a-bigger-margin-in-2024-amit-shah%2Farticleshow%2F105219533.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20To%20Expect%20When%20Biden%20Meets%20Xi%20Jinping%20In%20San%20Francisco%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EU.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20will%20meet%20on%20Wednesday%20before%20a%20summit%20of%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(APEC)%20forum%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20seeking%20to%20reduce%20friction%20in%20what%20many%20see%20as%20the%20world's%20most%20dangerous%20rivalry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20of%20the%20world's%20two%20largest%20economies%20have%20known%20each%20other%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20have%20shared%20hours%20of%20conversation%20in%20six%20interactions%20since%20Biden's%20January%202021%20inauguration.%20But%20they%20have%20met%20only%20once%20in%20person%20since%20then%20and%20Xi%20has%20not%20visited%20the%20United%20States%20since%202017%20when%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20issues%20are%20they%20likely%20to%20discuss%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20says%20the%20aim%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20to%20be%20held%20at%20an%20unannounced%20location%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area%2C%20is%20to%20boost%20communication%20to%20prevent%20an%20intense%20rivalry%20from%20veering%20into%20conflict.%20The%20meeting%20is%20expected%20to%20cover%20global%20issues%20from%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20to%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20North%20Korea's%20ties%20with%20Russia%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20human%20rights%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Bfair%26quot%3B%20trade%20and%20economic%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20is%20expected%20to%20tell%20Xi%20that%20the%20U.S.%20remains%20committed%20to%20standing%20with%20its%20allies%20and%20partners%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Chinese%20pressure%20against%20democratically%20governed%20Taiwan%2C%20which%20China%20claims%20as%20its%20own%2C%20and%20in%20the%20South%20and%20East%20China%20Seas.%20He%20will%20also%20express%20a%20specific%20commitment%20to%20the%20security%20of%20the%20Philippines%2C%20U.S.%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20deals%20can%20we%20expect%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20says%20Washington%20is%20looking%20for%20specific%20outcomes%20and%20hopes%20to%20see%20progress%20in%20reestablishing%20military-to%20military%20ties%20with%20China%20and%20in%20combating%20the%20trade%20in%20the%20potent%20synthetic%20opioid%20drug%20fentanyl%2C%20the%20use%20of%20which%20has%20become%20a%20scourge%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20Any%20deal%20on%20fentanyl%20would%20likely%20mean%20Washington%20having%20to%20lift%20human%20rights%20sanctions%20on%20China's%20police%20forensic%20institute%20in%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20his%20goal%20would%20be%20to%20resume%20normal%20communications%20with%20China%2C%20including%20military-to-military%20contacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20elections%20in%20Taiwan%20in%20early%202024%2C%20political%20analysts%20expect%20China%20to%20seek%20U.S.%20assurances%20that%20it%20will%20do%20nothing%20to%20encourage%20pro-independence%20elements%2C%20while%20Xi%20will%20also%20be%20hoping%20to%20persuade%20Biden%20to%20ease%20up%20on%20tariffs%20and%20the%20export%20controls%20that%20aim%20to%20keep%20the%20most%20advanced%20semiconductors%20from%20being%20sent%20to%20China.%20In%20a%20separate%20dinner%20with%20business%20leaders%2C%20the%20Chinese%20president%20will%20also%20been%20looking%20to%20boost%20flagging%20investment%20by%20U.S.%20firms%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20may%20highlight%20plans%20to%20increase%20commercial%20flights%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20policy%20experts%20said%20they%20could%20move%20to%20ease%20restrictions%20on%20journalist%20visas%2C%20which%20would%20be%20to%20the%20benefit%20of%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20is%20also%20expected%20urge%20China%20to%20use%20its%20influence%20with%20Iran%20to%20not%20broaden%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20one%20is%20expecting%20a%20reset%20of%20the%20relationship%20or%20any%20grand%20bargain%20that%20will%20dramatically%20alter%20how%20the%20countries%20see%20each%20other.%20%26quot%3BWe%20remain%20in%20an%20enduring%20period%20of%20competition%20and%20tension%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Richard%20Fontaine%20of%20Washington's%20Center%20for%20a%20New%20American%20Security.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20any%20big%20breakthroughs%2C%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20real%20change%20in%20substance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20the%20meeting%20impact%20markets%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarket%20participants%20will%20kee