%20more%20tools%20than%20banks%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20helping%20people%20buy%20homes.%3Cp%3Ejhorrocks%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETaylor%20Morrison's%20COO%20said%20builders%20can%20often%20offer%20homebuyers%20better%20rates%20on%20a%20newly%20built%20house.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EErik%20Heuser%20said%20builders%20can%20offer%20closing%20cost%20assistance%2C%20rate%20buydowns%2C%20and%20extended-lock%20rates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHeuser%20said%20the%20company%20is%20focusing%20on%20using%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20arrow%20in%20the%20quiver%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20buyers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20all%20know%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20competitive%20housing%20markets%20in%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh%20mortgage%20rates%2C%20home%20prices%20teetering%20near%20an%20all-time%20high%2C%20and%20historically%20low%20inventory%20are%20keeping%20many%20buyers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sellers%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20sidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Erik%20Heuser%2C%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20homebuilder%20Taylor%20Morrison%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20more%20and%20more%20hopeful%20buyers%20are%20looking%20at%20newly%20built%20homes.%20He%20said%2C%20typically%2C%20new%20homes%20would%20account%20for%20around%2012%25%20to%2013%25%20of%20total%20homes%20sold%20across%20the%20US%2C%20but%20today%20they%20make%20up%20more%20than%2025%25.%20The%20larger%20share%20of%20new%20homes%20on%20the%20market%20means%20paying%20a%20mortgage%20rate%20around%207%25%20isn't%20the%20only%20way%20into%20a%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeuser%20explained%20that%20folks%20who%20choose%20to%20finance%20their%20home%20purchase%20through%20their%20bank%20are%20going%20to%20get%20whatever%20that%20bank's%20rate%20is.%20But%20%26quot%3Bwe%20as%20homebuilders%20are%20able%20to%20offer%2C%20really%20it's%20four%20tools%26quot%3B%3A%20closing%20cost%20assistance%3B%20a%20temporary%20rate%20buydown%2C%20which%20is%20a%20lower%20initial%20payment%3B%20a%20permanent%20rate%20buydown%2C%20which%20is%20a%20higher%20upfront%20cost%20but%20provides%20a%20lower%20payment%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20loan%3B%20and%20extended-lock%20rates%20for%20homes%20that%20are%20under%20construction%2C%20where%20the%20homebuilder%20is%20%26quot%3Bable%20to%20provide%20security%20on%20what%20the%20rate%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Heuser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20buying%20a%20new%20home%20may%20be%20the%20most%20affordable%20way%20into%20homeownership%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Ftaylor-morrison-home-corporation-nyse-133945656.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethird-quarter%20earnings%20call%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Taylor%20Morrison%20explained%20that%20it's%20attracting%20%26quot%3Bwell-qualified%20consumers%20even%20among%20our%20first-time%20homebuyers%26quot%3B%20and%2088%25%20of%20its%20buyers%20are%20using%20its%20financing%20assistance.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20contributing%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20sales%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20Heuser%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHomebuilders%20like%20Taylor%20Morrison%20are%20able%20to%20offer%20lower%20mortgage%20rates%20than%20banks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Taylor%20Morrison%20is%20trying%20to%20understand%20the%20barriers%20to%20homeownership%2C%20whether%20it's%20the%20down%20payment%2C%20the%20monthly%20payment%2C%20or%20the%20overall%20sales%20price%2C%20and%20then%20using%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20arrow%20in%20the%20quiver%20to%20help%20them%20get%20into%20a%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%2C%20would-be%20buyers%20may%20have%20more%20luck%20securing%20a%20lower%20rate%20if%20they%20buy%20a%20new-construction%20home.%20In%20fact%2C%20there's%20even%20the%20possibility%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomebuilders-incentives-top-financing-tricks-by-tawn-kelley-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esecuring%20a%20rate%20as%20low%20as%204.8%25%20when%20buying%20a%20new%20home%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freddiemac.com%2Fpmms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20typical%20rate%20right%20now%20is%20above%207%25%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Freddie%20Mac.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFinance%20sells%20homes%2C%20and%20a%20house%20doesn't%20become%20a%20home%20unless%20we%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20get%20that%20customer%20to%20the%20closing%20table%2C%20and%20they%20can%20qualify%20and%20confidently%20make%20their%20mortgage%20payments%2C%26quot%3B%20Tawn%20Kelley%2C%20mortgage%20industry%20veteran%20and%20the%20president%20of%20financial%20services%20at%20Taylor%20Morrison%2C%20previously%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeeting%20buyers%20where%20they're%20looking%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20South%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20a%20third%20of%20homes%20on%20the%20market%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20were%20new%20builds%2C%20up%20from%20just%2017%25%20in%20the%20same%20quarter%20in%202019%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redfin.com%2Fnews%2Fnew-construction-homes-one-third-of-inventory%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20Redfin%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20that%20homebuilders%20are%20constructing%20more%20single-family%20homes%20now.%20Would-be%20sellers%20are%20effectively%20trapped%20in%20their%20homes%3A%20Existing%20homeowners%20see%20steep%20mortgage%20rates%20and%20a%20dearth%20of%20homes%20for%20sale%2C%20and%20worry%20about%20finding%20a%20new%20place%20to%20live.%20So%20they're%20holding%20onto%20their%20existing%20properties%2C%20pushing%20up%20the%20share%20of%20new%20homes%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20homes%20are%20more%20prevalent%20in%20the%20South%2C%20according%20to%20Redfin%2C%20an%20area%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus