icer%20at%20Discovery%20Education%2C%20says%20AI%20can%20make%20mundane%20tasks%20easier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20policies%20and%20guardrails%20can%20help%20empower%20employees%20exploring%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20Q%26amp%3BA%20is%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BCXO%20AI%20Playbook%26quot%3B%20series%20%E2%80%94%20straight%20talk%20from%20business%20leaders%20on%20how%20they're%20testing%20and%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDiscovery%20Education%20is%20a%20midsize%20learning-technology%20company%20with%20products%20designed%20to%20support%20teachers%20and%20students%20in%20kindergarten%20through%2012th%20grade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunch%20of%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20supercharged%20conversations%20about%20innovation%2C%20the%20company%20created%20a%20policy%20for%20testing%20and%20using%20artificial%20intelligence.%20It's%20designed%20to%20help%20employees%20understand%20the%20limits%20of%20what%20they%20can%20do%20and%20what%20the%20company%20leaders'%20expectations%20are%20for%20them%20to%20learn%20and%20adopt%20new%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20employees%20are%20looking%20for%20guardrails%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pete%20Weir%2C%20Discovery%20Education's%20chief%20product%20officer.%20%26quot%3BOur%20employees%20want%20to%20understand%3A%20Is%20the%20expectation%20that%20I'm%20using%20every%20single%20technology%20that's%20coming%20out%20there%20because%20I%20need%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20Weir%20about%20the%20company's%20use%20of%20generative%20AI%20to%20minimize%20mundane%20tasks%20and%20improve%20productivity%2C%20as%20well%20as%20guardrails%20to%20help%20employees%20explore%20and%20innovate%20without%20taking%20on%20AI%20projects%20beyond%20the%20company's%20scope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20Q%26amp%3BA%20with%20Weir%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20you%20do%20at%20Discovery%20Education%2C%20and%20when%20did%20you%20start%20exploring%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20at%20the%20company%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20job%20is%20to%20bring%20all%20the%20parts%20of%20product%20development%20together%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20we're%20building%20solutions%20that%20work%20for%20teachers%20and%20kids%20across%20content%2C%20curriculum%2C%20and%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20looking%20closely%20at%20large%20language%20models%20nine%20to%2012%20months%20before%20ChatGPT%20came%20out%20and%20were%20stunned%20when%20we%20saw%20how%20good%20it%20had%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20you%20identify%20ways%20to%20deploy%20generative-AI%20applications%20at%20Discovery%20Education%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertainly%20we%20have%20machine%20learning%20and%20AI%20as%20part%20of%20our%20products.%20But%20we%20started%20asking%20ourselves%20what%20are%20tasks%20that%20happen%20over%20and%20over%20again%20where%20we%20are%20constrained%20from%20doing%20things%20quickly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20challenges%20has%20always%20been%20how%20to%20know%20that%20we're%20working%20on%20the%20right%20things%20in%20the%20right%20context.%20We%20have%20millions%20of%20kids%20and%20teachers%20using%20our%20products%2C%20and%20we%20get%20open-text%20feedback%20from%20all%20kinds%20of%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20helps%20us%20build%20all%20that%20feedback%20into%20themes%20a%20lot%20faster%2C%20instead%20of%20going%20through%20reams%20of%20Excel%20files%20and%20trying%20to%20relate%20different%20datasets%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20tangible%20opportunities%20we%20see%20%E2%80%94%20taking%20those%20bridging%20tasks%20that%20eat%20up%20our%20team's%20time%20and%20focusing%20them%20more%20on%20bringing%20solutions%20to%20problems%20our%20teachers%20and%20kids%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20it%20easier%20to%20think%20of%20ways%20to%20use%20AI%2C%20since%20you're%20already%20steeped%20in%20technology%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20of%20change%20in%20this%20space%20is%20faster%20than%20anything%20I've%20seen%20in%20my%20career.%20It's%20really%20about%20understanding%20where%20you%20want%20to%20place%20your%20bets.%20It%20feels%20sometimes%20like%20you%20could%20work%20on%20something%20for%20six%20weeks%20and%20then%20it's%20obsolete%20because%20there's%20a%20new%20way%20of%20doing%20things%20that's%20come%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20mantras%20we%20have%20is%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20be%20a%20hammer%20looking%20for%20a%20nail.%26quot%3B%20What's%20a%20problem%20that%20we've%20always%20wanted%20to%20solve%20that%20a%20large%20language%20model%20can%20now%20make%20better%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20question%20we%20have%20to%20keep%20asking%20ourselves%2C%20because%20as%20technologists%20it's%20very%20easy%20to%20get%20drawn%20into%20how%20compelling%20the%20technology%20is.%20It's%20harder%20to%20take%20a%20step%20back%20and%20say%20why%20is%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20or%20the%20application%20of%20it%20in%20this%20specific%20area%20compelling%20as%20a%20solution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20need%20to%20reinvent.%20Zoom%20came%20out%20with%20a%20feature%20where%20it%20can%20record%20a%20video%20and%20provide%20a%20summary%20%E2%80%94%20so%20we%20as%20a%20company%20probably%20shouldn't%20be%20trying%20to%20work%20on%20our%20own%20proprietary%20version%20of%20transcribing%20videos%20after%20a%20Zoom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20great%20to%20get%20too%20far%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%2C%20because%20it%20might%20be%20a%20problem%20that%20people%20with%20far%20more%20resources%20are%20going%20to%20solve%20on%20your%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20have%20you%20organized%20your%20teams%20to%20foster%20and%20manage%20AI%20innovation%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20executive%20team%20here%20at%20Discovery%20Education%2C%20our%20responsibility%20is%20to%20know%20where%20and%20how%20we're%20applying%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20like%20a%20hub-and-spoke%20model%20for%20us%20%E2%80%94%20decentralize%20it%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20with%20some%20guardrails%2C%20and%20then%20have%20someone%20who's%20kind%20of%20in%20the%20know%20at%20all%20the%20places%20we're%20trying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20important%20aspect%20for%20us%20was%20having%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-regulation-necessary-ted-lieu-america-chatgpt-openai-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20our%20internal%20employees%20knew%20what%20is%20appropriate%20use.%20In%20a%20very%20short%20period%2C%20anybody%20could%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20things%20and%20send%20data%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20places.%20One%20thing%20I%20would%20encourage%20people%20to%20do%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20where%20you're%20sending%20data%20is%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20think%20about%20what%20steps%20we've%20taken%2C%20that%20policy%20and%20discussion%20across%20the%20different%20functions%20and%20executive%20functions%20were%20important.%20For%20someone%20who%20works%20very%20closely%20with%20an%20engineering%20team%2C%20we%20probably%20have%20a%20bias%20to%20understand%20these%20things.%20You%20take%20it%20for%20granted%20the%20exposure%20you%20have%20in%20product%20development%20and%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20things%20was%20a%20big%20zoom-out%20on%20how%20this%20is%20going%20to%20affect%20all%20of%20us.%20It%20is%20going%20to%20affect%20our%20customers%3F%20How%20do%20we%20think%20about%20it%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20from%20HR%20to%20recruiting%2C%20and%20how%20do%20we%20apply%20the%20technology%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20advice%20do%20you%20have%20for%20a%20company%20that's%20just%20getting%20started%20on%20its%20own%20AI%20journey%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20important%20not%20to%20focus%20too%20much%20on%20your%20actual%20products%20and%20services%20but%20on%20all%20the%20ancillary%20benefits%20you%20can%20have%2C%20and%20talk%20about%20those%20cross-functionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20one%20of%20the%20smartest%20things%20we%20did%20very%20early%20on.%20You%20can%20encourage%20someone%20who%20may%20not%20have%20thought%20of%20a%20generative-AI%20application%20as%20benefiting%20them%20or%20similarly%20didn't%20see%20a%20risk%20that%20others%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20dialogue%20has%20been%20constant%20for%20us%2C%20where%20we%20continue%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20we're%20applying%20it%20and%20what%20are%20the%20ethical%20uses%20of%20it%2C%20particularly%20in%20our%20industry%2C%20and%20then%20codifying%20that%20in%20a%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20bureaucratic%20as%20that%20sounds%2C%20what%20we%20found%20is%20our%20employees%20are%20looking%20for%20guardrails.%20Our%20employees%20want%20to%20understand%3A%20Is%20the%20expectation%20that%20I'm%20using%20every%20single%20technology%20that's%20coming%20out%20there%20because%20I%20need%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20it%3F%20Where%20are%20we%20on%20that%20risk%20curve%2C%20and%20what%20do%20you%20expect%20from%20me%20as%20an%20employee%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20for%20us%20was%20to%20explain%20to%20our%20employees%20how%20we%20frame%20the%20use%20of%20this%20technology.%20In%20our%20industry%2C%20it's%20not%20meant%20to%20replace%20the%20teacher%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20meant%20to%20augment%20the%20teacher.%20If%20we're%20doing%20this%20well%2C%20it's%20seamless%20and%20people%20don't%20feel%20like%20AI%20is%20a%20verb.%20It's%20something%20that's%20just%20making%20you%20more%20efficient%20or%20better%20at%20what%20our%20purpose%20is%2C%C2%A0which%20is%20to%20help%20educate%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20a%20company%2C%20not%20a%20business%20unit%2C%20when%20we%20think%20about%20this.%20We're%20in%20it%20together%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20have%20an%20open%20dialogue%20about%20the%20evolving%20use%20and%20benefit%20of%20the%20technology.%20It's%20a%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-helps-employees-according-to-a-chief-product-officer-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699993552000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65528f89385143459e8c37cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-helps-employees-according-to-a-chief-product-officer-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Generative%20AI%20has%20helped%20Pete%20Weir%2C%20the%20chief%20product%20officer%20of%20Discovery%20Education%2C%20alleviate%20mundane%20tasks%20and%20empower%20employees%20at%20the%20company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhood%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Hood)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-helps-employees-according-to-a-chief-product-officer-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rescuers%20use%20Bhojpuri%20on%20walkie-talkie%20to%20keep%20calm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699993539000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105217680%2Cimgsize-1065392.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fchar-dham-tunnel-collapse-rescuers-interact-via-walkie-talkie-at-times-in-bhojpuri-to-keep-calm%2Farticleshow%2F105217673.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rescue%20authorities%20in%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20in%20Dehradun%20are%20maintaining%20constant%20communication%20with%20the%20trapped%20laborers%2C%20speaking%20to%20them%20every%20hour%20to%20keep%20them%20calm%20and%20motivated.%20The%20workers%2C