nt%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20UK%20Home%20Secretary%20Suella%20Braverman%2C%20sacked%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20quit%20her%20office%20today%20with%20a%20massive%20parting%20shot%20--%20a%20scathing%20resignation%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20where%20she%20accused%20him%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bweak%26quot%3B%20and%20failing%20to%20deliver%20on%20key%20policies%20and%20keep%20their%20promise%20to%20the%20British%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20she%20wrote%20in%20the%20three-page%20letter%2C%20got%20the%20office%20partly%20because%20of%20her%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20agreed%20to%20support%20you%20because%20of%20the%20firm%20assurances%20you%20gave%20me%20on%20key%20policies...%20our%20deal%20was%20no%20mere%20promise%20over%20dinner%2C%20to%20be%20discarded%20when%20convenient%20and%20denied%20when%20challenged%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20rejection%20of%20this%20path%20was%20not%20merely%20a%20betrayal%20of%20our%20agreement%20but%20a%20betrayal%20of%20your%20promise%20to%20the%20nation%20that%20you%20would%20do%20'whatever%20it%20takes'%20to%20stop%20the%20boats%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BEither%20your%20distinctive%20style%20of%20government%20means%20you%20are%20incapable%20of%20doing%20so.%20Or%2C%20as%20I%20must%20surely%20conclude%20now%2C%20you%20never%20had%20any%20intention%20of%20keeping%20your%20promises%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bpromises%26quot%3B%20she%20accused%20Mr%20Sunak%20of%20breaking%20include%20reduction%20of%20illegal%20migration%2C%20stopping%20the%20migrant%20boats%20from%20crossing%20the%20English%20Channel%2C%20issuing%20statutory%20guidance%20to%20schools%20protection%20of%20biological%20sex%20and%20deliver%20on%20the%20north%20Ireland%20protocol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20needs%20to%20be%20honest%3A%20your%20plan%20is%20not%20working%2C%20we%20have%20endured%20record%20election%20defeats%2C%20your%20resets%20have%20failed%20and%20we%20are%20running%20out%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20letter%20spoke%20of%20Wednesday's%20much-anticipated%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20on%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20government's%20plan%20to%20send%20asylum%20seekers%20to%20Rwanda%20and%20described%20Mr%20Sunak's%20rejection%20of%20the%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20European%20Convention%20on%20Human%20Rights%20as%20a%20way%20to%20push%20through%20the%20scheme%20a%20%26quot%3Bbetrayal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20opted%20instead%20for%20wishful%20thinking%20as%20a%20comfort%20blanket%20to%20avoid%20having%20to%20make%20hard%20choices.%20This%20irresponsibility%20has%20wasted%20time%20and%20left%20the%20country%20in%20an%20impossible%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Braverman%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuella%20Braverman%20was%20sacked%20after%20the%20comments%20she%20made%20last%20week%20about%20the%20police's%20handling%20of%20a%20pro-Palestinian%20march.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20article%20she%20wrote%20published%20by%20The%20Times%2C%20she%20had%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20%26quot%3Bplaying%20favourites%26quot%3B%20during%20protests%20and%20claimed%20they%20largely%20ignored%20%26quot%3Bpro-Palestinian%20mobs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20wrote%20that%20she%20did%20not%20believe%20the%20protests%20were%20%26quot%3Bmerely%20a%20cry%20for%20help%20for%20Gaza%26quot%3B%20but%20were%20more%20an%20%26quot%3Bassertion%20of%20primacy%20by%20certain%20groups%20--%20particularly%20Islamists%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20Labour%20Party%20alleged%20it%20had%20increased%20tension%20at%20pro-Palestinian%20rallies%20and%20Mr%20Sunak%20came%20under%20increasing%20pressure%20to%20drop%20her%20from%20his%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20AFP)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699984260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F00v2vkf_suella-braverman_625x30