u%20ask%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20mogul%20said%20that%20everyone%20will%20have%20a%20personal%20assistant%20that%20can%20do%20almost%20anything%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20technology%20can%20even%20arrange%20whole%20trips%20for%20its%20users.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20asked%2C%20it%20will%20recommend%20things%20to%20do%20based%20on%20your%20interests%20and%20propensity%20for%20adventure%2C%20and%20it%20will%20book%20reservations%20at%20the%20types%20of%20restaurants%20you%20would%20enjoy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gates%20said.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20this%20kind%20of%20deeply%20personalized%20planning%20today%2C%20you%20need%20to%20pay%20a%20travel%20agent%20and%20spend%20time%20telling%20them%20what%20you%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20remarks%20come%20as%20the%20world%20is%20witnessing%20advancement%20in%20AI%20technology%2C%20with%20the%20emergence%20of%20new%20platforms%20like%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%2C%20Microsoft's%20Bing%2C%20Google%20Bard%20and%20Elon%20Musk's%20Grok.%20Mr%20Gates%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20AI%20tools%20will%20%26quot%3Bdo%20even%20more%26quot%3B%20than%20productivity%20tools.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20an%20idea%20for%20a%20business%2C%20an%20agent%20will%20help%20you%20write%20up%20a%20business%20plan%2C%20create%20a%20presentation%20for%20it%2C%20and%20even%20generate%20images%20of%20what%20your%20product%20might%20look%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20will%20be%20able%20to%20make%20agents%20available%20for%20their%20employees%20to%20consult%20directly%20and%20be%20part%20of%20every%20meeting%20so%20they%20can%20answer%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20no%20single%20company%20will%20dominate%20the%20agent%20business.%20He%20did%20point%20out%20that%20most%20AI%20agents%20in%20the%20future%20will%20probably%20be%20available%20at%20a%20price.%20Mr%20Gates%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B(But)%20if%20the%20number%20of%20companies%20that%20have%20started%20working%20on%20AI%20just%20this%20year%20is%20any%20indication%2C%20there%20will%20be%20an%20exceptional%20amount%20of%20competition%2C%20which%20will%20make%20agents%20very%20inexpensive.%20Today%2C%20agents%20are%20embedded%20in%20other%20software%20like%20word%20processors%20and%20spreadsheets%2C%20but%20eventually%20they'll%20operate%20on%20their%20own.%20Whether%20you%20work%20in%20an%20office%20or%20not%2C%20your%20agent%20will%20be%20able%20to%20help%20you%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20personal%20assistants%20support%20executives%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-founder%20of%20Microsoft%20claimed%20the%20technology%20will%20be%20utilised%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20purposes%20to%20simplify%20life%2C%20performing%20more%20intricate%20activities%20than%20those%20which%20are%20performed%20by%20voice%20assistants%20today.%20He%20asserted%20that%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20help%20with%20%C2%A0%26quot%3Bvirtually%20any%20activity%20and%20any%20area%20of%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20friend%20just%20had%20surgery%2C%20your%20agent%20will%20offer%20to%20send%20flowers%20and%20be%20able%20to%20order%20them%20for%20you.%20If%20you%20tell%20it%20you'd%20like%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20your%20old%20college%20roommate%2C%20it%20will%20work%20with%20their%20agent%20to%20find%20a%20time%20to%20get%20together%2C%20and%20just%20before%20you%20arrive%2C%20it%20will%20remind%20you%20that%20their%20oldest%20child%20just%20started%20college%20at%20the%20local%20university%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699980720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F28nkia78_bill-gates-reuters_625x300_10_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbill-gates-predicts-everyone-will-have-ai-personal-assistant-in-5-years-reality-to-change-completely-4574382%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bil