2title%22%3A%22'Power'%20Play%3F%20Congress%20Accuses%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20Of%20Electricity%20Theft%2C%20Case%20Filed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20month%20after%20he%20accused%20the%20Congress%20government%20of%20creating%20an%20artificial%20power%20shortage%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20a%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20Janata%20Dal(Secular)%20leader%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20for%20allegedly%20lighting%20up%20his%20house%20on%20Diwali%20using%20stolen%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20the%20case%20was%20registered%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20tweeted%20a%20video%20of%20electricity%20being%20drawn%20from%20a%20pole%20outside%20the%20former%20chief%20minister's%20residence%20at%20JP%20Nagar%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20power%20decorative%20lights%20for%20Diwali.%20In%20a%20sarcastic%20post%20with%20the%20video%2C%20the%20party%20had%20said%20its%20government%20was%20providing%20the%20Griha%20Jyoti%20scheme%20for%20200%20units%20of%20free%20electricity%20and%20wondered%20why%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20was%20resorting%20to%20%26quot%3Bcheap%20theft%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenying%20any%20theft%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20leader%20has%20said%20that%20a%20private%20decorator%20had%20connected%20the%20lights%20to%20the%20pole%20to%20test%20them%20and%20he%20had%20got%20them%20linked%20to%20his%20electricity%20meter%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20found%20out.%20Apologising%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bindiscretion%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20asked%20the%20electricity%20distributor%2C%20Bangalore%20Electricity%20Supply%20Company%20Limited%20(BESCOM)%2C%20to%20issue%20a%20notice%20and%20said%20he%20would%20pay%20the%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20against%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20was%20filed%20by%20BESCOM%20at%20Bengaluru's%20Jayanagar%20Police%20Station%20under%20the%20Indian%20Electricity%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20posted%20by%20the%20Congress%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20shows%20a%20wire%20linking%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy's%20residence%20and%20an%20electricity%20pole%20outside%20it.%20Shot%20both%20during%20daylight%20and%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20it%20also%20shows%20the%20house%20and%20some%20trees%20in%20the%20compound%20illuminated%20with%20Diwali%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world's%20most%20honest%20man%2C%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20has%20been%20illegally%20connecting%20his%20JP%20Nagar%20residence%20to%20the%20electric%20pole%20to%20draw%20electricity%20for%20Diwali%20lights.%20It%20is%20a%20tragedy%20that%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20has%20become%20a%20victim%20of%20electricity%20theft!%20Dear%20%40hd_kumaraswamy%2C%20our%20government%20is%20giving%20200%20units%20free%20to%20homes%2C%20not%202%2C000%20units!%20If%20they%20were%20so%20desperate%2C%20they%20could%20have%20applied%20for%20the%20Griha%20Jyoti%20Scheme%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Karnataka%20Congress%20handle%20posted%20in%20Kannada%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMocking%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20and%20stating%20that%20he%20may%20not%20have%20known%20that%20only%20one%20meter%20is%20allowed%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20the%20Congress%20accused%20him%20of%20using%20stolen%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20spite%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20even%20though%20we%20have%20taken%20measures%20to%20provide%20seven%20hours%20of%20electricity%20to%20the%20farmers%2C%20are%20you%20facing%20such%20a%20'drought'%20that%20you%20need%20to%20resort%20to%20such%20cheap%20theft%3F%20Didn't%20you%20hold%20a%20press%20conference%20and%20say%20'Karnataka%20is%20in%20the%20dark'%20and%20now%20you%20have%20lit%20your%20house%20with%20stolen%20electricity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20your%20house%20is%20shining%20like%20this%2C%20why%20do%20you%20say%20that%20Karnataka%20is%20in%20the%20dark...%20You%20seem%20to%20want%20a%20'Diwali'%20by%20robbing%20the%20people%20of%20the%20stat