A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20home%20ministry%20has%20extended%20the%20existing%20ban%20on%20eight%20%E2%80%9CMeitei%20extremist%20organisations%E2%80%9D%2C%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%2C%20for%20advocating%20the%20secession%20of%20Manipur%20from%20India%20through%20an%20armed%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20UAPA%20law%2C%20the%20Centre%20called%20them%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunlawful%20association%E2%80%9D%20while%20accusing%20them%20of%20inciting%20people%20of%20Manipur%20for%20secession%2C%20a%20government%20notification%20issued%20on%20Monday%2C%20November%2013%2C%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eight%20outfits%20are%20namely%2C%20the%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Liberation%20Army%20widely%20known%20as%20PLA%2C%20and%20its%20political%20wing%2C%20the%20Revolutionary%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Front%20(RPF)%3B%20the%20United%20National%20Liberation%20Front%20(UNLF)%20and%20its%20armed%20wing%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Army%20(MPA)%3B%20the%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Revolutionary%20Party%20of%20Kangleipak%20(PREPAK)%20and%20its%20armed%20wing%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Red%20Army%E2%80%99%3B%20the%20Kangleipak%20Communist%20Party%20(KCP)%20and%20its%20armed%20wing%2C%20also%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Red%20Army%E2%80%99%3B%20the%20Kanglei%20Yaol%20Kanba%20Lup%20(KYKL)%3B%20the%20Coordination%20Committee%20(CorCom)%3B%20and%20the%20Alliance%20for%20Socialist%20Unity%20Kangleipak%20(ASUK).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmha-extends-ban-on-10-meitei-extremist-organisations-under-uapa-for-another-five-year%2Farticle67528452.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20notification%20said%20the%20outfits%20have%20been%20engaging%20in%20activities%20prejudicial%20to%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%20by%20employing%20and%20engaging%20in%20armed%20means%20to%20achieve%20their%20objectives.%20Towards%20this%20end%2C%20they%20have%20been%20attacking%20and%20killing%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20police%20and%20civilians%20in%20Manipur.%20They%20are%20also%20indulging%20in%20acts%20of%20intimidation%2C%20extortion%2C%20and%20looting%20of%20the%20civilian%20population%20for%20collection%20of%20funds%2C%20the%20notification%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisations%20have%20also%20been%20accused%20of%20making%20contacts%20with%20sources%20abroad%20to%20influence%20public%20opinion%20and%20for%20securing%20their%20assistance%20by%20way%20of%20arms%20and%20training%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20achieving%20their%20secessionist%20objective%20and%20maintaining%20camps%20in%20neighbouring%20countries%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20sanctuaries%2C%20training%2C%20and%20clandestine%20procurement%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extended%20ban%2C%20which%20came%20into%20effect%20on%20November%2013%2C%20will%20remain%20in%20force%20for%2010%20years%20hence.%20According%20to%20the%20previous%202018%20notification%2C%20the%20said%20outfits%20were%20involved%20in%20756%20violent%20incidents%20from%20January%201%2C%202013-%20July%2031%2C%202018%2C%20and%20killed%2086%20persons%2C%20including%2035%20security%20personnel%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20notification%2C%20however%2C%20omitted%20reference%20to%20the%20number%20of%20violent%20incidents%20the%20organisations%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699971348000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F10074930%2FNorth_Block_Ministry_of_home_affairs-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentre-extends-ban-against-eight-meitei-extremist-organisations-for-10-years%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Calling%20them%20'unlawful%20association'%20under%20the%20UAPA%20law%2C%20the%20MHA%20notification%20said%20the%20outfits%20have%20been%20inciting%20people%20of%20Manipur%20for%20secession.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentre-extends-ban-against-eight-meitei-extremist-organisations-for-10-years%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Braving%20Threats%20by%20Land%20Mafia%2C%20Techie%20Turns%2025-Acre%20Barren%20Land%20Into%20a%20Forest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Gudiyatham%20in%20Vellore%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20G%20Srikanth%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature.%20He%20would%20walk%20to%20school%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332580%2Fmillet-based-startups-helping-farmers-ragi-jowar-international-year-of-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassing%20a%20forest%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20the%20way%2C%20and%20would%20enjoy%20listening%20to%20the%20chirping%20birds%20and%20insects.%20After%20an%20idyllic%20childhood%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20Chennai%20and%20worked%20as%20an%20assistant%20director%20in%20the%20movies.%20He%20recalls%20coming%20home%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98concrete%20jungle%E2%80%99%20to%20take%20a%20whiff%20of%20fresh%20air.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20every%20visit%20to%20Gudiyatham%20felt%20different.%20Srikanth%20saw%20the%20green%20cover%20reduce%20slowly%3B%20all%20but%20vanishing%20in%20front%20of%20his%20eyes.%20He%20felt%20disheartened%20that%20his%20hometown%20was%20also%20becoming%20like%20a%20big%20city%2C%20devoid%20of%20its%20natural%20beauty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20a%20tragic%20incident%20changed%20the%20trajectory%20of%20the%20computer%20science%20graduate%E2%80%99s%20life.%20His%20older%20brother%2C%20Sridhar%2C%20died%20in%20an%20accident%2C%20leaving%20Srikanth%20to%20move%20back%20home.%20He%20started%20working%20in%20the%20fields%20with%20his%20father%2C%20a%20farmer.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20his%20dream%2C%20to%20increase%20the%20green%20cover%20of%20his%20hometown.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20by%20planting%201%2C000%20trees%20in%202018%2C%20today%20the%2034-year-old%20has%20planted%20over%2015%2C000%20trees%20in%20Vellore%2C%20creating%20three%20forests.%20On%20the%20way%2C%20he%20has%20faced%20threats%20by%20the%20land%20mafia%20and%20politicians%2C%20had%20his%20trees%20cut%2C%20been%20beaten%2C%20but%20nothing%20has%20shaken%20him.%20He%20stands%20firmly%20on%20his%20resolve%20that%20he%20is%20giving%20back%20to%20Mother%20Nature%2C%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so%2C%20come%20what%20may.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20a%2025-acre%20barren%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Srikanth%20transformed%20a%2025%20acre%20land%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334096%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20land%20before%20and%20after%20Srikanth%20planted%207%2C000%20trees.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202018%2C%20Srikanth%20started%20planting%201%2C000%20trees%20on%20the%20roadside%20of%20Ulli%20village%20in%20Gudiyatham.%20He%20also%20took%20responsibility%20for%20maintaining%20the%20trees%2C%20and%20in%20six%20short%20months%2C%20they%20grew%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20used%20to%20be%20a%20social%20forest%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Palar%20river%2C%20that%20I%20would%20cross%20on%20my%20way%20to%20school%20every%20day.%20It%20was%20slowly%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20land%20mafia%20and%20all%20the%20trees%20were%20cut.%20It%20became%20a%20barren%20wasteland%20which%20was%20just%20used%20for%20sand.%20I%20wanted%20to%20restore%20and%20recreate%20that%20forest%2C%20which%20was%20home%20to%20so%20many%20birds%2C%20insects%20and%20monkeys.%20I%20would%20keep%20giving%20petitions%20to%20the%20district%20collector%20every%20week%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srikanth%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20social%20forestry%20is%20to%20involve%20locals%20of%20the%20region%20in%20the%20afforestation%20of%20unused%20wastelands%2C%20and%20to%20also%20protect%20and%20preserve%20them%20from%20rapid%20deforestation.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20social%20forest%2C%20people%20can%20come%20and%20go%20unlike%20a%20reserved%20forest%2C%20where%20no%20one%20is%20allowed%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Srikanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20saw%20many%20monkeys%20getting%20hurt%20on%20the%20roads%2C%20which%20bothered%20him%20greatly.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20birds%20and%20monkeys%20would%20be%20wounded.%20They%20had%20no%20place%20to%20go%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%201%2C000%20trees%20that%20he%20planted%20grew%20well%2C%20his%20efforts%20were%20noticed%20by%20the%20local%20authorities%20and%20reached%20the%20attention%20of%20then%20collector%2C%20A%20Shanmuga%20Sundaram.%20Srikanth%20recalls%20that%20Sundaram%20offered%20him%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20Sundaram%20to%20help%20him%20build%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20no