%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20cut%20or%20uproot%20the%20trees%20the%20evening%20we%20planted%20them.%20Almost%20800%20trees%20were%20cut%20off%20by%20this%20mafia.%20They%20would%20threaten%20me%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20call%20me%20to%20their%20office%20to%20intimidate%20me%2C%20and%20offer%20me%20money%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20this%20land.%20When%20I%20was%20clearing%20the%20land%2C%20they%20threw%20sand%20on%20me%2C%20as%20the%20entire%20village%20watched.%20They%20even%20threatened%20my%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Srikanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%20entire%20ordeal%2C%20Srikanth%20remained%20calm%20and%20said%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fight%20back%2C%20as%20he%20knew%20that%20what%20he%20was%20doing%20was%20for%20the%20greater%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20collector%20saw%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20help%20Srikanth%20recover%20the%20land%20and%20build%20a%20forest.%20Srikanth%20got%20back%20the%20encroached%2025-acre%20land%2C%20cleaned%20it%20and%20planted%207%2C000%20trees%20in%20the%20area.%20He%20spent%20more%20than%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20collector%20gave%20me%2027%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20workers%20to%20help%20me%20with%20the%20work.%20In%20a%20year%2C%20the%20forest%20grew%20well%20and%20became%20home%20to%20many%20birds%20and%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srikanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHe%20planted%20native%20trees%20and%20fruits%20in%20the%20forest%2C%20like%20jamun%2C%20peepal%2C%20fig%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201040px)%20100vw%2C%201040px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Srikanth%20invested%20Rs%201.5%20lakhs%