-more-than-a-cricket-match%2Fa-67070026%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%E2%80%99m%20pretty%20sure%20the%20concerned%20people%20are%20taking%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20avoid%20these%20kind%20of%20situations.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20ideal%2C%20everyone%20knows%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problems%20at%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20are%20also%20not%20good%20news%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20image%20as%20an%20up-and-coming%20sporting%20nation%20that%20wants%20to%20host%20the%202036%20Olympic%20Games.%20The%20images%20of%20a%20smog-ridden%20Delhi%20certainly%20don%E2%80%99t%20help%20that%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%2C%20smog%2C%20artificial%20snow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20becoming%20increasingly%20common%20to%20see%20elite%20sport%20affected%20by%20environmental%20and%20climate%20changes%2C%20the%20author%C2%A0David%20Goldblatt%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Australian%20Open%2C%20which%20was%20played%20in%20a%20heatwave%2C%20you%20had%20like%20a%20thousand%20people%20being%20treated%20for%20heat%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20Goldblatt%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20you%20know%2C%20Tokyo%202020%2C%20we%20had%20outdoor%20swimmers%20swimming%20in%20really%20health-threatening%2030-degree%20(86%20F)%20water.%20One%20of%20these%20events%20is%20going%20to%20be%20cataclysmic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoldblatt%20is%20the%C2%A0co-founder%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fsoccer%2Ft-64665526%5C%22%3EFootball%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Future%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20challenges%20football%E2%80%99s%20stakeholders%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20changing%20world.%20He%20believes%20that%20sport%20will%20have%20to%20change%2C%20replacing%20relentless%20growth%20with%20reduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20bigger%20question%20is%20really%20over%20the%20next%20kind%20of%2020%20years%3B%20global%20sport%20as%20a%20whole%2