%2Ft-17351918%5C%22%3EOlympics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sport%20is%20also%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fopinion-the-climate-crisis-sport-is-both-victim-and-sinner%2Fa-51999856%5C%22%3Eoffender%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20symbolically%20insane%2C%E2%80%9D%20Goldblatt%20said%20of%20the%202030%20World%20Cup.%20As%20a%20football%20fan%2C%20he%20sympathises%20with%20opening%20the%20tournament%20in%20Uruguay%2C%20but%20said%20a%20tournament%20with%20105%20matches%20on%20three%20continents%2C%20with%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20fans%20traveling%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20was%20a%20farce%20from%20an%20environmental%20point%20of%20view.%20Although%20sports%20associations%20such%20as%20the%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20and%20FIFA%20are%20making%20efforts%20to%20label%20their%20events%20as%20%E2%80%9Cclimate-friendly%E2%80%9D%20or%20even%20%E2%80%9Cclimate-neutral%E2%80%9D%20by%20paying%20for%20CO2%20compensation%20programs%2C%20Goldblatt%20said%2C%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20a%20plausible%20plan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20both%20FIFA%20and%20the%20IOC%20have%20committed%20to%20more%20climate%20protection%20as%20part%20of%20the%20World%20Climate%20Conference.%20The%20declared%20goal%20of%20the%20sports%20action%20plan%3A%20Greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20are%20to%20be%20halved%20by%202030%20and%20reduced%20to%20zero%20by%202040.%20Further%20talks%20are%20scheduled%20for%20the%20upcoming%20COP%2028%20world%20climate%20summit%20in%20Dubai%20at%20the%20end%20of%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20voices%20needed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECricket%E2%80%99s%20governing%20body%20has%20not%20yet%20signed%20up%20to%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20action%20plan%20but%20has%20set%20its%20own%20sustainability%20goals.%20The%20smog-ridden%20World%20Cup%20shows%20how%20necessary%20it%20is%20for%20sport%20to%20be%20a%20role%20mo