rim%20committee%20led%20by%20Ranatunga%20was%20installed.%20However%2C%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20intervened%2C%20reinstating%20the%20original%20board%20a%20day%20later.%20This%20reinstatement%20was%20facilitated%20by%20a%2014-day%20stay%20order%20of%20the%20earlier%20gazette%20that%20had%20dissolved%20the%20board.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Silva%E2%80%99s%20elected%20board%20currently%20has%20the%20reins%20at%20SLC%2C%20Ranasinghe%20is%20pursuing%20avenues%2C%20including%20the%20ICC%E2%80%99s%20dispute%20resolution%20committee%2C%20to%20lift%20the%20suspension.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20the%20ICC%20suspended%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20cricket%20board.%20Though%20officially%20termed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwarning%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20decision%20raises%20eyebrows%20regarding%20the%20extent%20of%20political%20interference%20in%20cricket%20governance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20being%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Fsri-lanka-cricket-suspended-by-icc-board-1408215%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuggested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20SLC%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Shammi%20Silva%2C%20itself%20requested%20the%20suspension%20to%20demonstrate%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20government%20that%20the%20ICC%20will%20not%20tolerate%20further%20meddling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20invoked%20reactions%20in%20the%20parliament%20of%20the%20country.%20Both%20the%20ruling%20and%20the%20opposition%20parties%20demanded%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20SLC.%20The%20parliament%20unanimously%20passed%20a%20resolution%20calling%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20SLC%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20recent%20parliamentary%20session%2C%20Sri%20Lankan%20MP%20Wimal%20Weerawansa%20had%20alleged%20that%20during%20the%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20India%2C%20it%20was%20former%20batsman%20Mahela%20Jayawardene%20who%20instructed%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20captain%20Kusal%20Mendis%20to%20bowl%20first%2C%20to%20the%20surprise%20of%20many.%20Such%20an%20instruction%20pointed%20to%20insidious%20connections%20ostensibly%20benefiting%20India%2C%20Weerawansa%20alleged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFuture%20under%20a%20cloud%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESri%20Lanka%20is%20set%20to%20host%20the%20Under-19%20cricket%20world%20cup%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%20However%2C%20the%20current%20crisis%20does%20not%20provide%20a%20favourable%20atmosphere%20for%20it.%20%3Cem%3EESPNCricinfo%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20ICC%20will%20take%20a%20decision%20about%20the%20U-19%20WC%20on%20November%2021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESLC%20president%20Silva%20has%20issued%20a%20warning%20that%20the%20country%20might%20lose%20the%20opportunity%20to%20host%20the%20competition.%20Silva%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20ICC%20wanted%20to%20suspend%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20July%2C%20but%20that%20he%20had%20prevented%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699961264000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14165545%2FUntitled-design-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Farjuna-ranatunga-sri-lanka-cricket-jay-shah%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sri%20Lankan%20government%20and%20its%20cricket%20board%20are%20at%20loggerheads%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20country's%20dismal%20performance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Farjuna-ranatunga-sri-lanka-cricket-jay-shah%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20War%20in%20Gaza%20Is%20Reshaping%20Geopolitics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23162231%2FGaza-building.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20has%20once%20again%20brought%20the%20Palestinian%20quest%20for%20a%20viable%20country%20to%20the%20forefront.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhow-hamas-attack-israel-unfolded-2023-10-07%2F%5C%22%3EHamas%20attack%20on%20October%207%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20retaliation%20have%20also%20destroyed%20the%20prospect%20of%20peace%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20anytime%20soon.%20As%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-gaza-palestinians-protests-europe-193a9aaca97df2c5c6a515f756a40a34%5C%22%3Epro-Palestinian%20protests%3C%2Fa%3E%20erupt%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Israeli%20onslaught%2C%20the%20threat%20of%20wider%20regional%20war%20seems%20all%20too%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestine-Israel%20conflict%20comes%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Abraham%20Accords%20in%20September%202020%20%E2%80%93%20so%20named%20for%20the%20patriarch%20of%20the%20three%20Abrahamic%20religions%20%E2%80%93%20signed%20between%20Israel%2C%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20Bahrain%2C%20facilitated%20by%20the%20US%20under%20then-President%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Accords%20recognised%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20Israel%20and%20established%20full%20diplomatic%20ties%20between%20the%20signatories.%20While%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20issue%20was%20consigned%20to%20the%20back%20burner.%20The%20Accords%20were%20followed%20by%20normalisation%20agreements%20between%20Israel%2C%20Morocco%20and%20Sudan%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20prospect%20of%20more%20Arab%20countries%20recognising%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fk5B1684GWJY%3Fsi%3Dcv0mDIo3siFeOaM6%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20continued%20the%20Middle%20East%20policy%20of%20Trump%20and%20took%20it%20to%20another%20level%20by%20trying%20to%20normalise%20relations%20between%20two%20hitherto%20implacable%20adversaries%20%E2%80%93%20Israel%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20a%20fear%20of%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20growing%20assertiveness%20also%20drove%20the%20Arab%20countries%20towards%20establishing%20friendly%20ties%20with%20Israel.%20These%20policy%20shifts%20inevitably%20meant%20backing%20away%20from%20their%20traditional%20position%20on%20Palestine%20and%20aligned%20well%20with%20US%20policy%20towards%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20the%20hopes%20and%20aspiration%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20turned%20to%20outrage%2C%20anger%20and%20despair.%20They%20were%20ignored%2C%20and%20the%20eruption%20of%20that%20anger%20is%20now%20all%20too%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20not%20really%20the%20%E2%80%98black-swan%E2%80%99%20event%20some%20have%20made%20it%20out%20to%20be.%20And%20its%20tremors%20now%20threaten%20to%20shift%20the%20tectonic%20plates%20of%20geopolitics%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20but%20also%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20basic%20assumption%20of%20the%20Abraham%20Accords%20%E2%80%93%20that%20there%20could%20be%20peace%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20without%20addressing%20the%20Palestinian%20question%20%E2%80%93%20has%20come%20unstuck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20Arab-Israel%20normalisation%20is%20in%20tatters.%20Even%20those%20Arab%20countries%20that%20sought%20to%20normalise%20ties%20with%20Israel%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20back%20off%20and%20criticise%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20today%20largely%20stand%20with%20the%20Palestinians.%20Most%20of%20them%20voted%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98humani